title: Soul Coaching Packages
description: Multi-session spiritual mentoring to explore and develop your intuitive gifts and multidimensionality. Available in 3, 5, or 8 sessions.
longdescription: Delve deeper into your spiritual journey with Denise's nurturing support and guidance. Over a series of sessions, Denise will guide, validate and offer unwavering support as you explore your intuitive gifts and multidimensionality. 3, 5 and 8 session packages available
